Signals Devtool is a powerful Chrome extension that enhances your web development workflow by providing real-time visualization and inspection of signals in your application. With this devtool, you can easily monitor and debug the flow of data through your application's signals.

𝐊𝐞𝐲 𝐟𝐞𝐚𝐭𝐮𝐫𝐞𝐬:
* Real-time visualization of signal values and changes
* Hierarchical tree view of signal dependencies
* Track change history.
